title: Ideal career progression for a masseuse (almost)
review: Jonah and Miles put up a great show in this latest Tod Phillips experiment. While it was very nice narration which made you laugh every now and then, I honestly have no great takeaways from this movie. It's just one of those movies that you can just watch on a boring Wednesday night. I did however like the part where they set up the premise for the upcoming segment like they would for a stage show
